@Node "Terms"

 @{u}4. Terms@{uu}


    The main terms used are:

        o stem or stemName: a valid ARexx variable name e.g. var,
          var.0, var.name

       o types of arguments: the types used are:
           D   any data            --
           N   numeric             /N
           S   symbol              /S ARexx valid symbol
           V   stemName            /V ARexx valid symbol as S but
                                      with length<20
@EndNode

@Node "Bugs"

 @{u}5. Bugs@{uu}


	This library should be considered a Beta version.
	The hack to rxsyslib.library is very deep and I
	don't really know if anything will be always ok.
@EndNode

